         <abstract>
            <p>Up to now, the rectangle discrepancy of linear congruential pseudorandom number generators could be exactly calculated only in some simple cases for a small number of generated points. Here an algorithm for the exact determination of the two-dimensional rectangle discrepancy is presented which is practicable for large generators and requires less computation time. The algorithm is based on special properties of linear congruential generators.</p>
          </abstract>
